            <p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="1">Too little, too late.<br>
<br>
Pet control was never a problem for the smart, experienced, and prepared.   This will breed nothing but more fat-n-dumb pet casters.<br>
<br>
The XP changes are good.  Remove the penality, and nix AFK xping in one shot.<br>
<br>
The pet agro changes sure lower the usefullness of Summon Companion.    Well, except in the odd poor pathing location.<br>
<br>
Oh well, they're trying I guess.</font></p>
             
